sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant C1 as Consumer 1 (Existing)
    participant C2 as Consumer 2 (New Joiner)
    participant GC as Group Coordinator (Broker)

    Note over C2: Consumer 2 Starts Up
    C2->>GC: JoinGroup Request (State: Empty/Join)
    Note over GC: Coordinator pauses group, triggers rebalance
    GC->>C1: JoinGroup Response (on next Heartbeat check)
    
    C1->>GC: JoinGroup Request
    Note over GC: Coordinator receives all JoinGroup requests
    Note over GC: Coordinator elects Group Leader (Consumer 1)
    
    GC->>C1: JoinGroup Response (Leader, Member Metadata)
    GC->>C2: JoinGroup Response (Follower)

    Note over C1: Leader runs Partition Assignor Strategy
    C1->>GC: SyncGroup Request (contains calculated assignments)
    C2->>GC: SyncGroup Request (empty assignment request)

    Note over GC: Coordinator persists assignments
    GC->>C1: SyncGroup Response (with assigned partitions)
    GC->>C2: SyncGroup Response (with assigned partitions)
    
    Note over C1,C2: Consumers begin polling their assigned partitions
